{"tid":2063363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［真正嘅黃色經濟］四川省廢除《查禁賣淫嫖娼活動的規定》","createTime":"2020-06-14T02:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T09:56:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9f89ab3ccfe3fd8fab77e655d427a61808bc85","tid":2063363,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"四川省人民代表大會常務委員會關於廢止《四川省查禁賣淫嫖娼活動的規定》的決定<br />\n<br />\n2020年06月13日 07:03:23 來源：四川日報 編輯：許成嵩<br />\n（2020年6月12日四川省第十三屆人民代表大會常務委員會第十九次會議通過）<br />\n<br />\n　　四川省第十三屆人民代表大會常務委員會第十九次會議決定：廢止《四川省查禁賣淫嫖娼活動的規定》。對賣淫嫖娼活動的查處依照有關法律、行政法規的規定執行。<br />\n<br />\n　　本決定自公佈之日起施行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://scnews.newssc.org/m/system/20200613/001077347.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscnews.newssc.org%2Fm%2Fsystem%2F20200613%2F001077347.html&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=15a0897d\" target=\"_blank\">http://scnews.newssc.org/m/system/20200613/001077347.html</a><br />\n<br />\n乜柒規定原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/四川省查禁卖淫嫖娼活动的规定\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E7%9C%81%E6%9F%A5%E7%A6%81%E5%8D%96%E6%B7%AB%E5%AB%96%E5%A8%BC%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=5b602cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/四川省查禁卖淫嫖娼活动的规定</a>"},{"pid":"8a28dd13f29a9a7408ed4d580994c6b3ca96d2b4","tid":2063363,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />窮了"},{"pid":"318ffa61a03917ae9d41d145174d67996b622736","tid":2063363,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"春江鴨早開工"},{"pid":"5f5f354eb7576f09d39d36b9baadbe0f95fe643f","tid":2063363,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:58:23.000Z","msg":"咁只會更多性病"},{"pid":"3ccdfe7a4b39